---
title: "SSD UC4 — Generate Personalized Story"
---
sequenceDiagram
    actor User as ":User"
    participant S as ":System"

    Note over User,S: System treated as BLACK BOX<br/>UC4 — Generate Personalized Story

    User->>S: selectMode(mode: "personalized")
    S-->>User: modeConfirmed, uploadPromptVisible: true

    User->>S: uploadReferencePhoto(photoFile)
    S-->>User: faceDetectionResult(faceDetected, confidence, gender)

    alt faceDetected = false
        S-->>User: warning("No face detected")
        User->>S: continueAnywayOrRetry(choice)
    end

    User->>S: setStoryOptions(genre, style, length)
    S-->>User: optionsConfirmed

    User->>S: submitPrompt(promptText)
    S-->>User: promptReceived, promptType

    alt promptType = "invalid"
        S-->>User: error("Invalid prompt")
    end

    loop system generating personalized story
        S-->>User: progressUpdate(stage, message)
    end

    S-->>User: storyGenerated(storyId, title, scenes[], pdfPath, mode: "personalized")
    Note right of S: All scene images maintain facial<br/>consistency via IP-Adapter FaceID
